description:
Discover British motorways in powerful speed machines, such as the villainous Jaguar F-Type SVR, the sleek Aston Martin Valhalla, and the agile Lotus Evija. 

This pack contains: 
- The Asphalt 9: Legends game
- Jaguar F-Type SVR -- blueprints to unlock
- Aston Martin Valhalla -- unlocked
- Lotus Evija -- unlocked
- 1,500,000 Credits
- 1,500 Tokens
